7.title: Google's new Trips app takes the stress out of planning vacations
7.text: Vacations are great. Planning them? Not so much. Google wants to make your life easy though with its new Trips app. It’s basically a giant travel guide and itinerary maker for trips to various locations around the world. Tell the app where you want to go, download the guide for offline use, and start planning. …
7.fallback: The Next Web: Google's new Trips app takes the stress out of planning vacations

text.2: Amen :joy::joy::joy: Sidder jo bare og griner.
